{"tid":2247021,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"（醫護界人士入黎幫幫小弟）","createTime":"2020-10-17T13:41:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-18T05:45:42.000Z","uid":185539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ee9f86ca2754dfd8c8d4054dd0bb01647b1dbcea","tid":2247021,"uid":185539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T13:41:53.000Z","msg":"有個問題問下大家<br />\n<br />\n小弟係公立醫院做完手術 <br />\n<br />\n我瞓個晚對面床個阿叔係咁咳又無戴口罩，<br />\n<br />\n起身發現我個口罩又帶得衰淨係遮住咗個嘴<br />\n<br />\n跟住起身個時有兩個護士行去對面個阿叔度<br />\n叫佢留痰驗野，話照到佢個肺有啲花，可能係肺癆<br />\n<br />\n跟住我即刻驚到瀨屎，問嗰兩個護士我可唔可以驗<br />\n佢哋同我講話隔咁遠冇事，（大概2米距離）<br />\n同埋無咩特別唔會幫我驗。<br />\n<br />\n然後同一日我就出左院了<br />\n依家食唔安瞓唔落，係咁查肺癆既野好驚呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n即刻好驚，依啲情況可以點做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f1912d87e80cb16fb15cbc69aca09b0ba6cf417","tid":2247021,"uid":343268,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T13:47:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e43afeae6c4411897f07f51d9bc9a71a01ff83c7","tid":2247021,"uid":114814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T13:50:38.000Z","msg":"乖乖地食足藥無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17c761efe4f57f1f1a407c499811eed50d7ddb9c","tid":2247021,"uid":185539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2f1912d87e80cb16fb15cbc69aca09b0ba6cf417","tid":2247021,"uid":343268,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T13:47:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T13:58:59.000Z","msg":"咁大鑊，可以去邊驗？"},{"pid":"652c4088c54b5ef7bda6d8b01cb818ddd689b8e4","tid":2247021,"uid":185539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e43afeae6c4411897f07f51d9bc9a71a01ff83c7","tid":2247021,"uid":114814,"like":1,"d